fields.value: Extracted Data From: Motor Vehicle Emission Simulator (MOVES)

dsDescriptionValue.value:
This submission includes a publicly available tool extracted in its original form. Please reference the Related Publication listed here for source and citation information

EPA's Motor Vehicle Emission Simulator is an emission modeling system that estimates emissions for mobile sources at the national, county, and project level for criteria air pollutants, greenhouse gases, and air toxics." [Quote from https://www.epa.gov/moves/latest-version-motor-vehicle-emission-simulator-moves]
